data.message: Style-to-archetype mapping for rapid design: Zen/Calm = Caregiver archetype (soft colors, generous whitespace, Sora/IBM Plex Mono). Fintech/Crypto = Outlaw archetype (dark mode, neon lime #BFFF00, sharp corners, JetBrains Mono). Luxury = Ruler archetype (gold #C9A962, Cormorant Garamond serif, deep black #0A0A0A). Kids/Playful = Innocent archetype (coral #FF6B6B, rounded corners 16-20px, Bricolage Grotesque). Sustainable/Organic = Creator archetype (terracotta #C67A52, warm cream #FAF8F4, IBM Plex Sans).
